 conventional beach.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><br />\r\n<strong>How to go:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Barguna can be reached by road and water from Dhaka. From Dhaka&#39;s Gabtali and Sayedabad, Druti Paribahan, Sakura Paribahan, Abdullah Paribahan and several other bus services ply this route.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And from Dhaka Sadarghat launch terminal M. V Yuvraj-2, MV Nusrat-2, M. V. Several other direct and local launches, including Yuvraj-4, leave for Barguna between 5pm and 6pm. The deck rent of these launches is 250 to 350 rupees and the single cabin rent is 800 to 1000 rupees. From Barguna you can go to Taltali Upazila by bus or motorbike to the evening beach located in Nishanbaria Union.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Where will you stay?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Among the residential hotels and rest houses in Barguna town are Zila Parishad Rest House, LGED Rest House, Water Development Board Rest House, Khamarbari Rest House, Public Works Department, Agro Service Center (0448-62728), CRP Rest. House (0448-62551), Barguna Rest House (01718-588856), Hotel Tajbin (0448-62503), Hotel Alam (0448-62234), Hotel Moumita (0448-62842), Hotel Falguni (0448-62733) etc.</p>\r\n', 4, 29, '44999808.jpg', '952072903.jpg', 'Shuvo-Sondha-Sea-Beach-Barguna-770x420.jpg', '', '', '', '', 1230, 0, '2022-06-29 11:47:06', 0, 0),
